stream << EOF
sidplay emulates the Sound Interface Device chip 
(MOS 6581, commonly called SID) and the 
Micro Processor Unit (MOS 6510) of the Commodore 64 on your computer.
It allows you to listen to more than 
17000 famous C64 game and demonstration musics.
EOF
